{"tid":1664343,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"預先為未來反抗 ,防將來地鐵加價，而家出閘時一齊大嗌","createTime":"2019-10-20T04:33:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T03:59:14.000Z","uid":60169,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0bc3e29b5a0cb2f977d46e09c22b77aca297b749","tid":1664343,"uid":60169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T04:33:57.000Z","msg":"又可以為未來準備， 又唔想咁順攤畀地鐵賺錢。<br />\n而家每一個人出入閘時一齊大嗌，<br />\n反對地鐵加價。<br />\n<br />\n又可以發洩不滿，又可以做和理非<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入閘嗌一次，出閘嗌一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae186c1692febe801a2f9871d1840818ab7b45c2","tid":1664343,"uid":278052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T04:34:37.000Z","msg":"其實都ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0baea812bde51d518745a8f03fb89f9539a086cb","tid":1664343,"uid":60169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T04:40:30.000Z","msg":"效果應該遠超不合作運動， 一日200萬人次就嗌咗200萬句。<br />\n<br />\n齊齊返工嗌一次收工呀一次， 見人嗌你又嗌一次，成個站都即刻生猛曬"},{"pid":"88bdb395545365e2ad8dad2ee797ec75f1f98c5f","tid":1664343,"uid":60169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T04:41:17.000Z","msg":"同埋最緊要完全合法， 除非政府用緊急法立地鐵站唔準大聲講嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da730445f1c5c779dc9f29cef7cd41b1d0e0bce7","tid":1664343,"uid":20222,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T04:42:13.000Z","msg":"大大聲叫反對地鐵加價<br />\n又可以掩蓋手足綠卡聲<br />\n一舉兩得"},{"pid":"6bb7389670268fb0dfef62e4b0b700a6504c01d9","tid":1664343,"uid":60169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"da730445f1c5c779dc9f29cef7cd41b1d0e0bce7","tid":1664343,"uid":20222,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T04:42:13.000Z","msg":"大大聲叫反對地鐵加價<br />\n又可以掩蓋手足綠卡聲<br />\n一舉兩得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T04:43:49.000Z","